high_descs: Walk across the room to the door.
Pick up the spatula next to the wine bottle, turn around and go to the end of the counter by the toaster.
Turn around and go to the end of the counter by the toaster and open the drawer under the toaster.
Put the spatula in the drawer and close the drawer.
Turn around and walk across the room to the table.
Pick up the spatula laying on top of the butter knife.
Turn around and walk back to the end of the counter by the toaster.
Open the drawer under the toaster, put the spatula inside the drawer, and close it
anns.task_desc: Put two spatulas into the drawer under the toaster.

high_descs: Walk forward until you hit the wall then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the spatula above the salt shaker.
Turn left and walk until you are almost past the counter to your left then turn left and walk so you are facing the right side of that counter then walk a step forward to face the counter.
Put the spatula in the drawer under the top of the counter.
Turn right and walk until you are almost at the wall then turn right and walk to the table.
Pick up the spatula to the right of the tomatoes.
Walk back to where you put the first spatula.
Put the spatula to the left of the other spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place two spatulas in a drawer.

high_descs: walk over to the right side of the kitchen counter
grab the spatula off of the counter
turn and walk over to the kitchen toaster
place the spatula inside the pull out drawer below the toaster
turn around and walk over to the kitchen table
grab the spatula off of the kitchen table
walk back over to the drawer below the kitchen toaster
place the spatula inside the pull out drawer to the left of the other spatula
anns.task_desc: put the spatulas back in the drawer
